---

---

<section class="section philosophy" id="philosophy">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-header fade-in">
            <h2 class="section-title">
                Plan, track, reflect.<br />Every month.
            </h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">
                Kakeibo is based on a budgeting method that dates back to 1904
                Japan. The idea is simple: awareness changes behavior. No
                spreadsheets, no algorithms: just you and your intentions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cycle">
            <div class="cycle-step fade-in">
                <div
                    class="cycle-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.12);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="28"
                        height="28"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--green)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <path d="M12 20h9"></path><path
                            d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="cycle-number">01</div>
                <h3>Plan</h3>
                <p>
                    At the start of each month, set your budget with intention.
                    How much will you earn? What are your fixed costs? What do
                    you want to save? Make a plan that reflects your values.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cycle-connector fade-in" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24" fill="none">
                    <path
                        d="M0 12h36M30 6l6 6-6 6"
                        stroke="var(--surface-light)"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cycle-step fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
                <div
                    class="cycle-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(17, 138, 178, 0.12);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="28"
                        height="28"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--blue)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polyline
                            points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="cycle-number">02</div>
                <h3>Track</h3>
                <p>
                    Throughout the month, log your spending. Each entry is a
                    moment of awareness. No auto-imports, no bank connections:
                    the act of recording is the point.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cycle-connector fade-in" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24" fill="none">
                    <path
                        d="M0 12h36M30 6l6 6-6 6"
                        stroke="var(--surface-light)"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="cycle-step fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
                <div
                    class="cycle-icon"
                    style="background: rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.12);"
                >
                    <svg
                        width="28"
                        height="28"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="var(--yellow)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                    >
                        <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"
                        ></path><path
                            d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="cycle-number">03</div>
                <h3>Reflect</h3>
                <p>
                    At month's end, review what happened. Did you keep your
                    promises? What surprised you? Reflection is where the magic
                    happens: it's how you learn and change your habits to spend
                    money in what really matters to you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .philosophy {
        background: var(--bg-elevated);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .cycle {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: var(--space-lg);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .cycle-step {
        flex: 1;
        max-width: 320px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .cycle-icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto var(--space-md);
    }

    .cycle-number {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--subtext);
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    }

    .cycle-step h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .cycle-step p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--subtext);
        line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .cycle-connector {
        padding-top: 34px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .cycle {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .cycle-connector {
            padding-top: 0;
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }

        .cycle-step {
            max-width: 400px;
        }
    }
</style>
